  <steps>
    <step num="0">In a medium mixing bowl, whisk together ¾ cup (225 g) chocolate hazelnut spread and the eggs. </step>
    <step num="1">Fold in the flour. </step>
    <step num="2">Evenly distribute into two mugs. </step>
    <step num="3">Microwave each mug for 2 minutes. </step>
    <step num="4">Cool for 5 minutes. </step>
    <step num="5">Frost with remaining chocolate hazelnut spread and serve warm. </step>
    <step num="6">Enjoy! </step>
  </steps>
